title: Top Places to visit in Dindori, Madhya Pradesh
content: Dindori is a district head office and a nagar panchayat in Dindori district in the state of Madhya Pradesh, India.Dindori has many historical as well as spiritual places. Some of the spiritual places are Laxman Madva, Kukarramath, Kalchuri Kali Mandir etc. The Kanha Tiger National Park is 180 km
